festival.introText:
Welcoming world-renowned international Rock artists to the County Town of Kent with cask ales, the best in worldwide street food, fairground rides, amazing entertainment and camping options – there really will be something for everyone!

Hosting two stages on both Saturday 22nd and Sunday 23rd July 2023, Maid of Stone Festival will bring both a main stage full of international artists and a second stage, showcasing the best UK and European acts, as well as highly regarded upcoming bands and local talent.

artists.name: Phil Campbell and the Bastard Sons

faqs.question: When is Maid of Stone Festival 2023?
faqs.answer: Maid of Stone Festival takes place Saturday 22nd July - Sunday 23rd July 2023.

faqs.question: Where is Maid of Stone Festival?
faqs.answer: Maid of Stone Festival will be held at Mote Park, Maidstone, Kent.
